<div class="container container--narrow" style="padding-top: var(--space-120); padding-bottom: var(--space-120);">
  <h1 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-64);">Our Story</h1>
  
  <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-64);">
    {{ 'lifestyle-2' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}
  </div>

  <div class="story-content" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-24);">
      AERIDIAN began as an isolated research project. The objective was singular: to create a textile matrix capable of withstanding extreme thermal shifts without sacrificing the visual discipline of luxury tailoring.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-24);">
      After 34 months of prototyping and field-testing in hostile climates, the initial core collection was finalized. Every artifact produced under the AERIDIAN marque is a testament to our obsession with absolute quality and zero compromise.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

